1.0.6 2026-01-10
 - feat: relocate test_db cloning directory to /var/tmp/test_db in Makefile to optimize I/O.
 - feat: add check-galera and check-repli targets to Makefile for cluster health monitoring.
 - fix: apply innodb_flush_method = O_DSYNC to fix ERROR 14 on WSL2.
 - feat: add tmpfs mount for /tmp to all Galera nodes.
 - feat: standardize Makefile commands to use mariadb host client instead of docker exec.

1.0.5 2026-01-09
 - fix: corrected emergency startup targets and replaced docker exec with mariadb host client.
 - feat: improve Galera cluster resilience with wsrep_slave_threads=1 and Flow Control tuning.
 - feat: implement make renew-ssl-repli for zero-downtime SSL rotation.
 - feat: optimize MariaDB configuration in gcustom_*.cnf with recommended parameters.
 - feat: add make inject-*-galera and make inject-*-repli for automated deployment and data injection.
 - docs: full translation of CONTEXT.md into English.

